query:
UPDATE nest_eggs
            SET
                author = $1, name = $2, description = $3,
                config_files = $4, config_startup = $5, config_stop = $6,
                config_script = $7, config_allocations = $8, startup = $9,
                force_outgoing_ip = $10, features = $11, docker_images = $12,
                file_denylist = $13
            WHERE nest_id = $14 AND id = $15
